### 配置自定義

播放器的所有文本標籤和圖標都可通過 `_data/xpPlayer.js` 進行自定義：

```javascript
export default {
	fallbackCover: "{{ xpPlayer.fallbackCover }}",
	labels: {
		playPause: "{{ xpPlayer.labels.playPause }}",
		showLyrics: "{{ xpPlayer.labels.showLyrics }}",
		currentTime: "{{ xpPlayer.labels.currentTime }}",
		duration: "{{ xpPlayer.labels.duration }}",
		playProgress: "{{ xpPlayer.labels.playProgress }}",
	},
	icons: {
		play: "{{ xpPlayer.icons.play }}",
		pause: "{{ xpPlayer.icons.pause }}",
		lyrics: "{{ xpPlayer.icons.lyrics }}",
	},
};
```

修改此文件後，所有使用播放器的頁面都會自動更新。

